1. to create a distribution/Release:
make a 
cvs co lpzrobots
cd lpzrobots
cvs update -dP
cd dist_utils
./createDist.sh

2. for extra lib bundle:
just start ./createextraDist.sh

3. for binary distribution:
take the prepared distribution from 1 and do
make prepare
make libs
cd oderobots/simulations
make all
cd oderobots/examples/
make all